Either a dark red or pale yellow, wine is made from the pressing of grapes that have been fermented and aged.
Spirits, usually made from distilled grains, are very potent and should not be taken lightly.
Skull Ale
A hollowed out skull containing a dark and somewhat strong smelling liquid. It's the specialty drink at the Salty Dog Tavern.
Broiled Spicy Greenfish

Greenfish are abundant in the seas that lap the coast of Nordock. While bland themselves, a concoction of pepper and other spices brings out a surprisingly tangy and pleasant flavor. This fish counts as a single food serving for resting purposes.
